        "text": "I've stumbled upon a similar problem. I can see the updated content if I read the feed manually, but the feed reader (Claws-Mail) insists there were no updates. Destroying the cached `ETag`, `Last-Modified` values to force a full download doesn't help, nor does changing the feed URL. It turns out that the feed silently fails to parse after a few entries. I've traced it to the feed entry for PR17886 containing invalid UTF-8 (`André` was encoded in Latin-1 in two places). If this keeps happening (it probably will), I'll pile on some more server-side hacks.",
